        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "block-157",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 157,
        "text": "随堂测试"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-158",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 158,
        "text": "登录仿真软件平台，练习站点经纬度、室内主设备、电源、传输、机柜高度等各项信息采集，完成后保存提交，交给老师课后检查。"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-159",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 159,
        "text": "直击难点"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-160",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 160,
        "text": "本节重点："
      },
      {
        "id": "block-161",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 161,
        "text": "基站室内都需要收集那些相关信息，练习仿真软件基本操作。"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-162",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 162,
        "text": "本节难点："
      },
      {
        "id": "block-163",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 163,
        "text": "GPS、坡度仪等测量工具使用。"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-164",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 164,
        "text": "二维码预留二维码预留"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-165",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 165,
        "text": "任务测评"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-166",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 166,
        "text": "1.基站室内需要采集那些信息？"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-167",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 167,
        "text": "2.GPS中显示搜索到几颗以上卫星才可用？GPS记录精度要求？"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-168",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 168,
        "text": "3.直流设备工作电压范围是多少？"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-169",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 169,
        "text": "4.在3GPP协议中规定的5G独立组网方式有那些？"
      },
      {
        "id": "block-170",
        "kind": "paragraph",
        "order": 170,
